Question 1) 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
How do I get GNOME running?

Answer 1) 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Place the following in your .xinitrc 
(copying the one from /etc/X11/xinit/ is advisable):

# start the window manager
PATH=@PREFIX@/bin:$PATH
exec gnome-session

See also:
http://trac.macports.org/wiki/GNOME#RunningGNOME
